                You can record your product, ingridients to make the product and the cost and profit you want
            </p>
            <a href="/product" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary font-weight-bold text-white">Record Your Product</a>
        </main>
    
        <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
            <p>&copy; 2022</p>
        </footer>
